## Hard rules

- **Never** push to `main` from any sub-repo. The hook will block it.
- **Never** edit `{{USER_SERVICE_PATH}}` from this workspace.
- **Never** mock the DB in integration tests (see `docs/CODING_PRACTICES.md`).
- **Never** target Flutter widgets by text in E2E specs — only by `Key()`.
- **Never** invent a tracker ID — paste the real one or leave `TODO: fill in` and surface it to the user.
- **Never** populate `prod/` `<FILL_IN_*>` placeholders by hand — run `/configure-prod` instead so the answers are recorded in `BOOTSTRAP.json` and other prod-conditional sections (workflows, CLAUDE.md) update consistently.
